一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"要有自信，第一件事要自己<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有料到</span></strong></ins><br />\n連自己都睇唔起自己，講嘢越嚟越細聲<br />\n人哋都廢鬼事睬你<br />\n<br />\n諗下自己有咩興趣/長處，係人冇你有嘅，而且係大家都睇得起嘅<br />\n俾三個月半年時間集中發展一下佢<br />\n自然有返自信<br />\n<br />\n講到尾自信因素絕對&gt;溝通技巧<br />\n<br />\n有三至六個月嘅時間<br />\n你仲可以執執①儀態②樣<br />\n前者pick up返你啲禮貌，相信你毒得自然唔mk得去邊<br />\n行路挺直，諗下威水嘢<br />\n頭就算唔望人都咪望地下<br />\n後者有錢嘅食補品用護膚品<br />\n冇錢嘅早睡早起+每日一個飯後果 (最好係橙)<br />\n得閒行下路跑下步<br />\n<br />\n做晒以上所有嘢先好去問人攞技巧經驗<br />\n或者去睇攻略秘笈<br />\n以上"},{"pid":"61224a55ac7e82677ac8056acc4892f5a10c2bcb","tid":887170,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88333579a4e2ae20db9db988c2edfae70bca5c91","tid":887170,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}